#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sarrera"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "What's &kteatime;?"
msgstr "Zer da &kteatime;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kteatime; is a handy timer for steeping tea. No longer will you have to "
"guess at how long it takes for your tea to be ready. Simply select the type "
"of tea you have, and it will alert you when the tea is ready to drink."
msgstr ""
"&kteatime; tea prestatzeko tenporizatzaile erabilgarri bat da. Aurrerantzean "
"ez duzu tea prest egoteko zenbat denbora falta den igartzen ibili beharko. "
"Hautatu daukazun te mota, eta edateko prest dagoenean oharraraziko zaitu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Use &kteatime;"
msgstr "Nola erabili &kteatime;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start up &kteatime;, it will automatically dock itself in your "
"panel. To access the menu, right click on the docked icon. This will present "
"a list of options which are covered in more detail in the next chapter."
msgstr ""
"&kteatime; abiarazten duzunean, automatikoki kairatuko da panelera. Menua "
"atzitzeko, eskuin botoiaz klikatu kairatutako ikonoa. Honek aukera zerrenda "
"bat aurkeztuko du, hurrengo atalean zehaztasun handiagoz azalduko dena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Timing Your Tea"
msgstr "Zure tearen denbora neurtzen"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Upon starting, the panel icon will be that of an tea mug. If you click with "
"the &RMB; on the mug and select your tea, an animated clock visualizing the "
"remaining time is displayed on the icon. After the specified time, the tea "
"will be finished, and a suitable message box will be shown. At this point, "
"you can close the message box by clicking on it. This resets also the timer "
"and the clock on the mug disappears again."
msgstr ""
"Hasterakoan, paneleko ikonoa te katilu bat izango da. &RMB;rekin katiluan "
"klik egin eta zure tea hautatzen baduzu, gelditzen den denbora irudikatzen "
"duen ordulari animatu bat bistaratuko da ikonoan. Zehaztutako denbora "
"amaitzean, tea prest egongo da, eta mezu egoki bat erakutsiko da. Puntu "
"honetan, mezu laukia itxi dezakezu bere gainean klik eginez. Honek "
"tenporizatzailea berrezartzen du eta katiluko ordularia atzera desagertzen "
"da."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "The timer should only be reset by those who really enjoy tea."
msgstr ""
"Tenporizatzailea tea gozatzen dutenek soilik berrezarri beharko lukete."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Options"
msgstr "Menuaren aukerak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following section describes the menu options that are available in "
"&kteatime;."
msgstr ""
"Hurrengo atalak &kteatime;-k eskuragarri dituen menu aukerak deskribatzen "
"ditu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Your Tea"
msgstr "Hautatu zure tea"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Clicking on the icon with the &RMB; will bring up a menu. At the top of "
#| "the menu there are three menu items. Here, you can select what kind of "
#| "tea you are preparing to drink. There are: <guimenuitem>Black Tea</"
#| "guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Earl Grey</guimenuitem>, and "
#| "<guimenuitem>Fruit Tea</guimenuitem>. These teas are preconfigured with a "
#| "default time. Many people have complained that the times are not correct. "
#| "Please be aware that the amount of time it takes to steep a cup of tea is "
#| "based on personal preference. The times chosen are approximations. If you "
#| "read on, you will learn how to change or delete these predefined times "
#| "and to set your own time. A quick-and-easy way to set a custom time is to "
#| "choose <guimenuitem>Anonymous...</guimenuitem> from the menu."
msgid ""
"Clicking on the icon with the &RMB; will bring up a menu. At the top of the "
"menu there are four menu items. Here, you can select what kind of tea you "
"are preparing to drink. There are: <guimenuitem>Black Tea</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Earl Grey</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Fruit Tea</guimenuitem>, "
"and <guimenuitem>Green Tea</guimenuitem>. These teas are preconfigured with "
"a default time. Many people have complained that the times are not correct. "
"Please be aware that the amount of time it takes to steep a cup of tea is "
"based on personal preference. The times chosen are approximations. If you "
"read on, you will learn how to change or delete these predefined times and "
"to set your own time. A quick-and-easy way to set a custom time is to choose "
"<guimenuitem>Custom...</guimenuitem> from the menu."
msgstr ""
"&RMB;rekin ikonoan klik egiteak menu bat gora ekarriko du. Menuaren "
"goialdean hiru menu elementu daude. Hemen, edateko prestatzen ari zaren te "
"mota hautatu dezakezu. Daudenak: <guimenuitem>Te beltza</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Earl Grey</guimenuitem>, eta <guimenuitem>Fruta tea</"
"guimenuitem>. Te hauek lehenetsitako denbora batekin aurrekonfiguratuta "
"daude. Jende ugari kexatu da denborak zuzen ez daudelakoan. Mesedez kontuan "
"izan te katilu bat prestatzeko denbora norberaren gustuen araberakoa dela. "
"Erabilitako denborak hurbilketak dira. Irakurtzen jarraitzen baduzu, "
"aurrezarritako denbora hauek nola aldatu edo ezabatu eta zure denbora "
"ezartzen ikasiko duzu. Nork bere denbora ezartzeko modu azkar eta erraza "
"menutik <guimenuitem>Anonimoa...</guimenuitem> hautatzea da."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guimenuitem>Configure Notifications...</guimenuitem> brings up the "
"&kde; Notification Settings for &kteatime;."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start the Tea Timer"
msgstr "Hasi te tenporizatzailea"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To start the tea timer select a tea from the context menu. As confirmation "
"that you have indeed started the timer, a clock visualizing the remaining "
"time is displayed in the panel icon."
msgstr ""
"Te tenporizatzailea hasteko hautatu te bat testuinguru menutik. "
"Tenporizatzailea hasi duzunaren baieztapen bezala, falta den denbora "
"erakusten duen ordulari bat bistaratzen da paneleko ikonoan."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure"
msgstr "Konfiguratu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item opens up the configuration dialog box. A screenshot is shown "
"below:"
msgstr ""
"Menuaren elementu honek konfiguratzeko elkarrizketa laukia irekitzen du. "
"Azpian pantaila argazki bat erakusten da:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The &kteatime; configuration dialog box.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kteatime; konfiguratzeko elkarrizketa laukia.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The &kteatime; configuration dialog box.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kteatime; konfiguratzeko elkarrizketa laukia.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As shown in the picture, you may add new entries for other tea or change "
"names, times and the order of existing entries. This is useful if you are "
"brewing a cup of tea that is not on the list or if you do not agree with the "
"predefined times. To edit one entry, mark it in the <guilabel>Tea List</"
"guilabel> on the left and change the values in the <guilabel>Tea Properties</"
"guilabel> on the right."
msgstr ""
"Irudian erakusten den bezala, beste te batzuren sarrera erantsi edo izenak, "
"denborak eta dauden sarreren ordena aldatu dezakezu. Erabilgarria da "
"zerrendan ez dagoen te katilukada bat prestatzen ari bazara edo aurrez "
"ezarritako denborarekin ez bazaude ados. Sarrera bat editatzeko, markatu "
"ezkerreko <guilabel>Te zerrenda</guilabel> elementu bat eta aldatu balioa "
"eskuineko <guilabel>Te propietateak</guilabel> atalean."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The box below is the <guilabel>Action</guilabel> field. Here you can "
#| "define an action that will be executed when the time is up. The "
#| "<guilabel>Notification</guilabel> check box enables the event selected in "
#| "the &kde; Notification Settings. The button <guibutton>Configure "
#| "Notifications...</guibutton> brings up the &kde; Notification Settings "
#| "for &kteatime;. If <guilabel>Popup</guilabel> is selected, a message box "
#| "will appear alerting you to the fact that your tea is ready."
msgid ""
"The box below is the <guilabel>Action</guilabel> field. Here you can define "
"an action that will be executed when the time is up. If <guilabel>Popup</"
"guilabel> is selected, a message box will appear alerting you to the fact "
"that your tea is ready."
msgstr ""
"Azpiko laukia <guilabel>Ekintza</guilabel> eremua da. Hemen denbora betetzen "
"denean exekutatuko den ekintza bat definitu dezakezu. "
"<guilabel>Jakinarazpena</guilabel> egiaztapen laukiak &kde; Jakinarazpen "
"ezarpenetan hautatutako gertakizuna gaitzen du. <guibutton>Konfiguratu "
"jakinarazpenak...</guibutton> botoiak&kteatime;-rentzako &kde; Jakinarazpen "
"ezarpenak gora ekartzen du. Baldin eta <guilabel>Azaleratu</guilabel> "
"hautatzen bada, mezu lauki bat agertuko da tea prest dagoela oharraraziko "
"dizuna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enable the check box labeled <guilabel>Visualize progress in icon "
"tray</guilabel>, the progress will be shown as a little animated clock "
"inside the icon."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Erakutsi aurrerapena ikono erretiluan</guilabel> etiketatutako "
"egiaztapen laukia gaitzen baduzu, aurrerapena ikono barruko ordulari animatu "
"txiki batekin erakutsiko da."

